@GRC.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5087

### Get Supported Countries
GET {{GRC.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/countries
Accept: application/json

###

### User Registration with Valid Data (India)
POST {{GRC.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationType": 0,
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass@123",
  "confirmPassword": "SecurePass@123",
  "roleType": 6,
  "mobileNumber": "9876543210",
  "countryCode": "91"
}

